A high-end boutique to cater for VIPs has opened near the Villa Rosa Kempinski Hotel.Euro Collections is on the ground floor of the Mirage.The store will officially be launched next Friday and will cater for plus-size people.Owner Maurice Owich said he opened the store because plus-size people struggle to find clothes."We import our products from Europe. In Europe you will find clothes that can fit everybody depending on the size. We are out to give our clients what fits them without the clients having to struggle too much," he said.